devdoc.title: Maintains a doubly linked list keyed by address.

contains(LinkedList.List storage,address.notice: Returns whether or not a particular key is present in the sorted list.

getKeys(LinkedList.List storage).notice: Gets all element keys from the doubly linked list.

headN(LinkedList.List storage,uint256).notice: Returns the N greatest elements of the list.

insert(LinkedList.List storage,address,a.notice: Inserts an element into a doubly linked list.

push(LinkedList.List storage,address).notice: Inserts an element at the end of the doubly linked list.

remove(LinkedList.List storage,address).notice: Removes an element from the doubly linked list.

update(LinkedList.List storage,address,a.notice: Updates an element in the list.
